### Arabic

ثُمَّ يَتُوبُ ٱللَّهُ مِنۢ بَعْدِ ذَٰلِكَ عَلَىٰ مَن يَشَآءُ ۗ وَٱللَّهُ غَفُورٌ رَّحِيمٌ

### English

Then afterwards Allah will turn in grace to whoever He wills. And Allah is All-Forgiving, Most Merciful.